rows.label: bf01050100_0010
rows.name: All right! Back to making money!

rows.label: bf01050100_0020
rows.name: I think this haul should be enough for today.

rows.label: bf01050100_0030
rows.name:
Oi, Gramps! Care for a little swim
to the Avaritia Trade Guild?

rows.label: bf01050100_0040
rows.name:
You're planning on selling it now?
It's getting toward my bedtime...

rows.label: bf01050100_0050
rows.name:
Don't play the lazy old man with me.
There's plenty of sunshine left!

rows.label: bf01050100_0060
rows.name:
Kids these days... No respect,
I swear...
